buy any uber equipment in the past (and also coz we are all wearing planes gear thanks to our connections with our previous guild)<br><br>So anyway... to summarise, this is not all about which gear is 'uber', this is a real fun way to hand out items for your twinks or to your very appreciative guildmates.<br><br>So go out there, stop leveling, and have fun!<br>Ta-Ta!<br><br>Xev<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
